{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b1f638dc6a","title":"来取围城打援办法敌有生力量","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c406a82f31","index":0,"year":1946,"month":10,"day":24,"articleId":"b1f638dc6a"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji22","name":"毛泽东全集第22卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji22.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji22":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"739f8f6fd7","type":"paragraph","text":"来取围城打援办法敌有生力量","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"b1f638dc6a"},{"id":"2af3f54eeb","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年10月24日）詹、李、王，并告程、李巴","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"b1f638dc6a"},{"id":"c17c75ed73","type":"paragraph","text":"你们作战方针应着重行灭敌有生力量，然后敌占各据点自然容易为我收复。为实行此方针，应采取围城打援办法。围城之目的不在得城，而在打援。集中七八倍于敌之兵力（例如集中四五个团打数援兵一个至二个营），每次事前均应有充分准备，不浪打，打则必胜。打时须用包围迁回，以期尽歼。此点对干部应作深刻教育","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"b1f638dc6a"},{"id":"1aecf4197f","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"b1f638dc6a"},{"id":"abe5d1cde4","type":"paragraph","text":"西敬[1]詹，指詹才芳，当时任冀东军区司令员。李，指李楚离，河北元氏人，当时任冀东军区政治委员。王，指王智涛，河北沧县人，当时任冀东军区参课长。[2]程、李，指程子华、李运昌，当时分别任翼热辽军区司令员兼政治委员和副司令员。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"b1f638dc6a"}],"page":{"id":"a941ffa42b","publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"b1f638dc6a","start":233,"end":233}}}},"__N_SSG":true}